aces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90db823ca61c3670d63da351029fd3dd8e404eba","tid":704100,"uid":22560,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"我想聽dodo 講野唔得？咁多個人入面擺明係麻利最低質啦，成日問埋啲無聊問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢都痴痴地線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地指出佢有問題，佢唔係諗點樣改善，而係鬧返人，仲話做藝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444df2a063aa7a037689c31a9f099684d09b9b36","tid":704100,"uid":115724,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:20:25.000Z","msg":"人地話你講野好難聽呀<br />\n你份工係DJ黎架 令聽者聽得舒服係你既份內事黎<br />\n<br />\n你拎個快餐店店員黎話樣衰有咩用<br />\n樣衰同做快餐店無直接掛勾<br />\n但係聽得好辛苦同你做DJ就相關<br />\n<br />\n再者 樣衰改不了 你講野難聽可以改<br />\n但係你串柒柒叫人唔好聽即係無意去改 無意去進步<br />\n垃圾DJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c52045ca064fb73fa8de17eaf65724d722a9ed","tid":704100,"uid":42601,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:22:19.000Z","msg":"叫人轉台 即係倒商台米?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3462e49051091b7ef18849af8642d9d561cb8e7a","tid":704100,"uid":167658,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:27:04.000Z","msg":"樓下間快餐店d野食本身好好食，生意好好，忽然轉左個員工入黎之後整d野食好似屎咁，客人越來越少......<br />\n<br />\n舊客好懷念以前嘅味道，叫果個員工自己走啦<br />\n之後個員工話你唔鍾意食可以唔黎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依情況係咁樣呀麻利</span></span>"},{"pid":"af654f407b9e87dfe0d95c3e7e6686d31f8ff9da","tid":704100,"uid":167658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T11:30:00.000Z","msg":"我寧願聽鍾雪同孟呢都唔想聽佢，新人都不如"},{"pid"